</exercise>
</note>
<note id="fs-id1428748" class="try">
<exercise id="fs-id1599944">
<problem id="fs-id1875231">
<para id="fs-id974965">Find the <span class="token">ⓐ</span> perimeter and <span class="token">ⓑ</span> area of the figure:</para><media id="fs-id1171513624489" alt="A square is shown comprised of 4 smaller squares.">
