<example id="fs-id1171505622642">
<exercise id="fs-id1785069"><problem id="fs-id1547656">
<para id="fs-id1901758">The area of a rectangular room is <m:math><m:mn>168</m:mn></m:math> square feet. The length is <m:math><m:mn>14</m:mn></m:math> feet. What is the width?</para>
