 <entry>Step 5. <emphasis effect="bold">Solve</emphasis> the equation.</entry>
 <entry><media id="eip-id1164271013482" alt="."><image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_BMath_Figure_09_04_075_img-03.png"/></media></entry>
